Package com.github.yjgbg.fun.valid.core

Interface StaticMethodReferenceGetter<A,​B>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - javaBean的类型
    B - get方法返回的类型
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.function.Function<A,​B>, java.io.Serializable
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
    @FunctionalInterface
public interface StaticMethodReferenceGetter<A,​B>
extends java.util.function.Function<A,​B>, java.io.Serializable
    表示一个javaBean中的get方法 用途：希望对路径有类型安全的表达，而不是拼接字符串

    例如: Role role = new User().getRole(); Getter<User,Role> getter = User::getRole; assert "role" == getter.propertyName();
